##########################################
# SCAR - example requests for the VS Code "REST Client" extension
# Open this file in VS Code and click "Send Request" above each request to execute it
# 
# Pre-requisites:
#   1. Install the "REST Client" extension in VS Code
#   2. Start the SCAR server (e.g. by running `docker compose up` in the SCAR project directory)
#   3. The admin key below (`dev-key`) matches the one in docker-compose.yml
#       SCAR_ADMIN_API_KEYS=dev-key:dev-operator. Reads need no auth.
##########################################

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@apiKey = dev-key
@sat = SAT-427

### liveness check
GET {{baseUrl}}/healthz

### bulk read
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/satellites/{{sat}}/assets?at=2025-06-01T00:00:00Z

### upload a JSON calibration asset (multipart: form-fields + JSON file part)
# @name uploadGains
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/v1/satellites/{{sat}}/assets/vicarious_cal_gains/versions
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----scarboundary

------scarboundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="valid_from"

2025-01-01T00:00:00Z
------scarboundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="vicarious_cal_gains.json"
Content-Type: application/json

< ../samples/vicarious_cal_gains.json
------scarboundary--


### Resolve that asset at a point in time
# Returns metadata + presigned MinIO URL for the payload bytes.
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/satellites/{{sat}}/assets/vicarious_cal_gains?at=2025-06-01T00:00:00Z


### Read back the version id captured from the upload response above
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/satellites/{{sat}}/assets/vicarious_cal_gains
# created version_id was: {{uploadGains.response.body.created.version_id}}


### Upload an open-ended JSON asset, then supersede it (truncates first)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/v1/satellites/{{sat}}/assets/body_to_payload/versions
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----scarboundary

------scarboundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="valid_from"

2020-01-01T00:00:00Z
------scarboundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="made-up.json"
Content-Type: application/json

{ "v": 1 }
------scarboundary--

### Supersede: a newer version from 2025 closes the 2020 version
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/v1/satellites/{{sat}}/assets/body_to_payload/versions
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----scarboundary

------scarboundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="valid_from"

2025-01-01T00:00:00Z
------scarboundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="fake.json"
Content-Type: application/json

{ "v": 2}
------scarboundary--


### Upload a frame (binary)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/v1/satellites/{{sat}}/assets/darkframe/versions
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----scarboundary

------scarboundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="valid_from"

2025-01-01T00:00:00Z
------scarboundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="micro_darkframe_newsat53.npy"
Content-Type: application/octet-stream

< ../samples/micro_darkframe_newsat53.npy
------scarboundary--


### Resolve the frame at a point in time
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/satellites/{{sat}}/assets/darkframe?at=2025-06-01T00:00:00Z

### Retire darkframe at 2030
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/v1/satellites/{{sat}}/assets/darkframe/versions/retire
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "effective_from": "2030-01-01T00:00:00Z" }

### After retirement, there is a gap -> no_asset_valid 422
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/satellites/{{sat}}/assets/darkframe?at=2031-01-01T00:00:00Z


### 
# Error cases
###

### Missing auth -> 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/v1/satellites/{{sat}}/assets/body_to_payload/versions
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----scarboundary

------scarboundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="valid_from"

2025-01-01T00:00:00Z
------scarboundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="fake.json"
Content-Type: application/json

{ "v": 4.27 }
------scarboundary--

### Timestamp w/o timezone -> 422 validation_error
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/v1/satellites/{{sat}}/assets/body_to_payload/versions
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----scarboundary

------scarboundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="valid_from"

2025-01-01T00:00:00
------scarboundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="fake.json"
Content-Type: application/json

{ "v": 4.27 }
------scarboundary--